aws s3 mb s3://iam-role-bucket-12345 --region ap-south-1


Create file & upload:

echo "Created from EC2 using IAM Role" > demo.txt
aws s3 cp demo.txt s3://iam-role-bucket-12345/demo.txt


ğŸ“Œ Interview Question:
Can EC2 access S3 without access keys?
âœ” Yes, using IAM Role with proper permissions.

Session 85 â€“ VPC (Networking)
What is VPC?

Virtual Private Cloud

Your own isolated network in AWS

Region-level service

CIDR Block

Example:

VPC: 10.0.0.0/16

Subnet: 10.0.1.0/24

ğŸ“Œ Interview:
CIDR defines IP range.

Subnets

Public subnet â†’ Internet access

Private subnet â†’ No direct internet

Availability Zone based.

Route Table
Destination	Target
10.0.0.0/16	Local
0.0.0.0/0	Internet Gateway
Internet Gateway

Enables internet access for public subnet EC2

NAT Gateway

Allows private subnet instances to access internet outbound only

VPC Setup Steps

Create VPC

Create Subnets

Create Internet Gateway

Create Route Table

Associate Route Table

VPC Peering (Test & Prod)

Connect two VPCs

Allows private IP communication

No overlapping CIDR allowed

ğŸ“Œ Interview:
VPC Peering is one-to-one and non-transitive.

